<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp25589072"><span class="os-number">8</span><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-problem-container"><p id="fs-idp25589200">Compare 1 mole of H<sub>2</sub>, 1 mole of O<sub>2</sub>, and 1 mole of F<sub>2</sub>.</p>
<p id="fs-idm34170816">(a) Which has the largest number of molecules? Explain why.</p>
<p id="fs-idm147492048">(b) Which has the greatest mass? Explain why.</p></div></div>
</div>
