<p id="fs-idm26438416">(c) 0.001 mg Cd<sup>2+</sup> in 0.100 L, the maximum permissible concentration of cadmium in drinking water</p>
<p id="fs-idm26437648">(d) 0.0079 g C<sub>7</sub>H<sub>5</sub>SNO<sub>3</sub> in one ounce (29.6 mL), the concentration of saccharin in a diet soft drink.</p>
</div></div>
